examples.en: After medical school, he worked as an intern at the university hospital.
The organisation can enjoin secrecy upon the internship student.
A summer internship will stand you in good stead when applying to college.
The internship offers only a pittance for a salary, but it is a great opportunity to gain experience.
Nearly every medical student is required to take an internship when he has completed medical school, regardless of his plans for his later career.
Mr. King spent the first week of the summer internship acquainting everyone with the new computers.
